RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM smvws_user_branches b WHERE b.User_id = global.user_id AND b.Branch_code = sypks_utils.get_branch(LBTB_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_REF_NO))

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_REF_NO = LBTBS_STP_EXCEPTION.BORROWER_REF_NO AND LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.PART_REF_NO = LBTBS_STP_EXCEPTION.PARTICIPANT_REF_NO AND LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.PART_ESN = LBTBS_STP_EXCEPTION.EVENT_SEQ_NO

LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_REF_NO = LBTBS_STP_STATUS_LOG.BORR_REF_NO AND LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_ESN = LBTBS_STP_STATUS_LOG.BORR_ESN AND LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.PART_REF_NO = LBTBS_STP_STATUS_LOG.PART_REF_NO

LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_REF_NO = LBVWS_STP_POSITIONS.BORR_REF_NO AND LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.PART_REF_NO = LBVWS_STP_POSITIONS.PART_REF_NO AND LBTBS_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_ESN = LBVWS_STP_POSITIONS.BORR_ESN

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT MIS_CODE, CODE_DESC from ((SELECT DISTINCT mis_code, code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code a, tltms_portfolio_expcode_master m, tltms_portfolio_expcode_detail d WHERE m.portfolio = d.portfolio AND d.expense_code = a.mis_code AND m.portfolio = ? AND active = 'A')UNION (SELECT DISTINCT mis_code, code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code a, tltms_portfolio_expcode_master m, tltms_portfolio_expcode_detail d, tltms_position_identifier e WHERE m.portfolio = d.portfolio AND m.portfolio = e.portfolio AND d.expense_code = a.mis_code AND e.position_identifier = ? AND active = 'A'))

select a.product_code, a.product_description,RTGS_PRODUCT from oltms_product a, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c where a.module = 'OL' and a.once_auth = 'Y' and a.product_code = c.product and a.product_type<>'D' order by a.product_code
